Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:01.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.97,0:00:03.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:05.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:09.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.85,0:00:13.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:14.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:17.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bird Master Princess Abi, who has\nallied herself with Naraku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.09,0:00:18.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}sends her demon birds to\nattack the village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:22.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The people worship a mysterious\nfigure in hopes of salvation...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that figure can't be...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:08.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess Abi, the Bird Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:10.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Create a path for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:16.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you order me around like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.48,0:02:23.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not an order. It's a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:30.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without any interruption\nfrom anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That is made from my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall lend it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:38.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.73,0:02:42.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:52.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?! They're attacking!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.51,0:02:55.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There're more of them coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:01.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-They're on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:07.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:09.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:11.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.43,0:03:17.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:18.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.40,0:03:20.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saimyosho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:27.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just who are you?\NWhy'd you interfere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:38.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I could say the same thing!\NAre you one of Naraku's minions?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.46,0:03:39.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:43.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Saimyosho flying around\nyou are proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.29,0:03:45.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:49.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on\nbetween you and Naraku,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you killed my birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:56.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll kill every one of you and\ndrain every drop of your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:57.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:00.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.22,0:04:05.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:08.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:10.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.49,0:04:12.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:13.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.59,0:04:14.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is this half-demon?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}His aura is stronger than I thought.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:34.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:38.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku is trying to find a way to\nget to the border
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,between this life and the next, in order\nto get the Sacred Jewel shard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:45.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And is collecting human blood\nsomehow connected to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's the only thing\nwe have to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.49,0:04:50.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever the {\i1}connection....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:02.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The path that leads to the border\nbetween this world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.98,0:05:06.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It will soon open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:42.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.45,0:05:44.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon birds!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:46.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:21.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa! Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:23.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:25.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To St. Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you two going too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:40.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then let's travel together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:43.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is this also the work\nof the demon birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:07.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They seem to be attacking\nevery village in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.30,0:07:14.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But that demon who called\nherself Princess {\i1}Abi....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:16.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is her purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:19.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, {\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:23.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What could she be up {\i1}to....{\i0}\ngathering so much human blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}dunno....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.05,0:07:26.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:26.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll find the nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:32.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nest? You mean the nest\nof the demon birds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:33.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:35.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We have nothing else\nto go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.96,0:07:38.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:48.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master {\i1}Jaken....{\i0}\NMaster {\i1}Jaken....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:52.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, oh why, are you green?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:56.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess we have to stay\nback again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:58.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't it boring, Master Jaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It really is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I didn't have to baby-sit\nthis kid,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could accompany\NLord Sesshomaru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:08.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:16.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not here to\nabduct Rin again, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:25.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Did I ever do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you dare deny it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't Sesshomaru around?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:33.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You fool! If Lord Sesshomaru\nwere here,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:35.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,your head would be\nrolling on the ground by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:38.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}guess....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:44.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did she want anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Guess he was right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:50.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I come empty-handed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.60,0:08:52.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}all I could expect is\nto be killed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't mess with me, brat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:13.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you in pain, Kagura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:19.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wasn't able to kill that brat\NHakudoshi with my Dance of Blades.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:23.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, in order to become free,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must kill Naraku and\NHakudoshi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold it...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:31.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then, when that infant\nbroke apart into two...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This was meant to happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:44.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was there a purpose for\nthat other half, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:47.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure of it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And a purpose more important\nthan Hakudoshi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:53.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why it was put into\nthe care of Kanna,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}who is trusted more than me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:58.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}There has to be some secret.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe something...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:04.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That could put an end\nto Naraku's life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:28.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:30.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why can I not hear\nthe baby's first cries?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.87,0:10:32.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and let me hold him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:36.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}lady....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:39.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Regretfully....the{\i0} young lord {\i1}was....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:42.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the heir was stillborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! Are you saying\nhe's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:48.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. He was not breathing\nwhen he was {\i1}born....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:50.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My {\i1}lady....{\i0}\NI am so {\i1}sorry....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:17.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:29.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The infant is not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The {\i1}infant....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:41.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:42.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How {\i1}frustrating....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:44.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not a single clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:49.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demon birds would likely\nnest in a high place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Princess Abi has Naraku's\nprotection.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:55.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe the nest is hidden\nby a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:00.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I'll rip through\nany damn barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:04.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but we have\nto find the barrier first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:05.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup! I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:07.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:10.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's like Naraku's leading\nus by the nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:16.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Inuyasha, look!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:19.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't go any further.\NYou go on without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang on, woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You escaped from the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, it was so frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:30.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We never knew when the\ndemon birds would {\i1}attack....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:33.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone in the region\nis packing up and leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are a godsend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.36,0:12:37.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It always ends up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:39.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you're used to it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you have a place to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:43.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:49.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If we appeal to St. Hijiri, the holy man\nwho lives beyond the pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.11,0:12:52.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,perhaps he can protect us\nfrom the demon birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:53.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,St. Hijiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:55.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he a priest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, no one knows\nfor sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:00.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We've only heard\nrumors about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems no one has\nactually seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.79,0:13:05.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:09.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His face is always\nhidden,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:11.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and no one has ever\nheard his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:14.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is said that communication\nbetween the holy man and the people
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:16.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,is conducted by his\nattendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:18.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So no one knows whether he is\nold or young,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:20.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,or even if he is male or female.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:25.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! You traveled this far relying\non rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:28.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait up! So everyone else is\ngoing there
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,because of these rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:31.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:33.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, I think we'd better hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:34.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because the birds appear\nwherever there are a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:41.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:41.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Thank you for carrying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When we reach a safe place,\NI'll put you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:01.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everyone, beyond this pass\nis the holy man's village!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:02.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:09.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Hakudoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you up to this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:15.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura, look\nat the bird food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:16.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Their blood, each drop of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:21.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,will create the road between\nthis world and the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:24.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:25.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems they've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:32.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.35,0:14:37.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:38.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:39.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:44.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:53.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura's Blades!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:57.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been a while, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:14:58.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi! Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:04.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:07.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,While you blabber,\nhumans will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:08.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:17.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:18.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't scatter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:19.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:27.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit! They keep coming!\NIs there no end?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:38.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as we're protecting\nthe villagers,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:40.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}we can't act freely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku, something is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:46.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know. Hakudoshi and\NKagura are merely watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:51.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the birds' actions seem\nas though they're just buying time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:53.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be {\i1}that....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right! There are probably\nmore people gathered
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:58.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,at St. Hijiri's village!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:02.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you finally\nfigured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:04.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:08.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By now, Abi and\nher main force of demon birds
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:11.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,have begun their attack\non this so-called holy man's village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then did you spread the rumors\nabout St. Hijiri?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do such a\ntiresome thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There is a holy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.15,0:16:25.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably just another\nexorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:27.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because they were so\nafraid of the demon birds,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:31.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,they raised him to god-like status\nand worshipped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:34.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We learned about him\nand we came to feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:36.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:40.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, you can cut it out,\nyou bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:49.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Countering your\NWind Scar takes no effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:51.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:00.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master, I can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:02.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The same demon birds are\nattacking the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give it up and just watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.71,0:17:20.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the foolish humans\nbecome bird fodder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:24.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your stupid {\i1}barrier....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:29.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,will be broken by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the Red Tetsusaiga\nthat breaks through barriers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:36.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:42.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whaa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:44.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:47.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even the Red Tetsusaiga\ncould not break the barrier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So even Inuyasha can't\nbreak through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:51.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:54.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn Hakudoshi,\nwhat does it take to kill you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:17:57.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:03.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:06.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:11.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that just now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:15.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The barrier is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:17.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's....not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:20.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:25.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:27.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:35.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:41.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura!\NWe leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:43.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.27,0:18:50.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:51.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave this to me\nand go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This way, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:18:59.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:15.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.57,0:19:27.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:31.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not working.\NThe horse's too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:47.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's too fast.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:51.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if we met head-on,\nhe'll just dodge my attacks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:52.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Might as well try it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:19:57.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:04.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All {\i1}right....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:05.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:24.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the end of the road,\nwild horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.03,0:20:28.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You may move with\nlightning speed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:30.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but this space is\ntoo small for you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:39.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what I've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:49.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.55,0:20:52.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Backlash Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.85,0:21:23.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:34.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.86,0:21:37.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sacred Arrow that\nbroke through Hakudoshi's barrier...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:45.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This arrow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:46.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}came from over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:52.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one's there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:47.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.43,0:23:48.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's as though they're\nlooking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.30,0:23:51.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are they looking for\nthe holy man?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:53.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard he decimated\NPrincess Abi's huge army of birds
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.44,0:23:55.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,with a single arrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:23:57.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it broke through\NHakudoshi's barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.41,0:23:58.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Naraku noticed this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:24:00.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does he intend to find out\nif this holy man is actually {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.98,0:24:02.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and if so, kill her once more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.85,0:24:04.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, he's definitely a\nhindrance to Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.88,0:24:09.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyash\N"The Mysterious Light that\NGuides the Saint"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.85,0:24:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Soul Collectors?\NIs Kikyo still alive?!
